Sarkozy Says Economy Needs ‘Healthy, Regulated’ Banks

-- B y   M a r k   D e e n
-- 
2011-10-23T15:24:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/sarkozy-says-economy-needs-healthy-regulated-banks.html
President  Nicolas Sarkozy  said the
European economy needs banks that are “healthy” and well
regulated.  “What’s important is that savings are protected and that
credit is provided to the economy,” Sarkozy said at a press
conference in Brussels.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mark Deen in Paris at 
